{"tid":1472652,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"所有重對大陸人有希望既人，請去開下大陸網站，睇下佢地點吊香港人","createTime":"2019-08-14T15:37:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T15:43:21.000Z","uid":199126,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6cc29dfee526e0129893a732ec50bc02dd4e0b4f","tid":1472652,"uid":199126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:37:26.000Z","msg":"係大陸人眼中，香港所有發生既事，衹有兩個字---港獨。係呢個大前提下，警暴係正確，港共一切都係正確。從來冇人願意睇下香港真相。香港人係以前為中國冇條件付出，換黎中國人一聲活該。<br />\n第一，香港人衹有香港人支援，唔好再相信中國人，咩同胞，香港人永不割席。<br />\n第二，將返送中造成記錄片，並加以翻譯，以各種方法分享至任何到港旅客(包括中國人)，以中立立場講解反送中運動，要世人睇清中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n第三，一世不信同敵視狗、正苦同某大國，從來冇人當你自己人，唔好自己走去做奴隸。香港人好善忘，但香港人好幾記仇。"},{"pid":"3f75ea342833b94d26bf1bbfba7170bf573edb7d","tid":1472652,"uid":15605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:41:15.000Z","msg":"記唔記得當年孔慶東點鬧香港人係狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"583645715419ebd67e30b07594286a1f2b2b297d","tid":1472652,"uid":54511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:42:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S5t3qg2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS5t3qg2.png&h=19bacde1&s={SIZE}\" /> 理燃佢地自己打飛機<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hz4YYCc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhz4YYCc.gif&h=ebe565ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b7e01aa1f1c54d706ac9640083835ee309cac58","tid":1472652,"uid":138144,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:43:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rxeVgoJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrxeVgoJ.jpg&h=960eefff&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sWdu5g4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsWdu5g4.jpg&h=a437423f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gb77RW5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/t